{"word":"H8058 - שָׁמַט - shâmaṭ - shaw-mat' - Discontinue","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁמַט</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâmaṭ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-mat'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Discontinue"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மிரளு, இடறு, விட்டுவிடு, கீழே தள்ளு, சும்மா கிடக்கவிடு, தள்ளுண்டுபோ"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to release, to let drop or loose or rest or fall"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to let drop or fall"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be made to fall down, to be thrown down"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to cause to let drop"},{"paragraph":"2) to release, to let drop"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>fling</i> down; incipiently to <i>jostle</i>; figuratively to <i>let alone</i>, <i>desist</i>, <i>remit: - </i>discontinue, overthrow, release, let rest, shake, stumble, throw down."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8058 - שָׁמַט - shâmaṭ - shaw-mat'/8058\">H8058</a>, <a href=\"#/H8059 - שְׁמִטָּה - shᵉmiṭṭâh - shem-it-taw'/8059\">H8059</a>"}]}